<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="J" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Jealousy" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Jealousy,</orth> 1) suspicion in love: <bibl n="shak. ven 1137" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 1137</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.4.177" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. II, 4, 177</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.1.104" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. II, 1, 104</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.1.104" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. II, 1, 104</bibl> <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.2.302" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 302</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.2.302" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 302</bibl> <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.3.201" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 201</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.5.73" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 5, 73</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.2.155" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 155</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.2.155" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 155</bibl> <bibl n="shak. wiv 5.1.20" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 20</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 2.1.102" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. II, 1, 102</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 2.1.102" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. II, 1, 102</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.1.81" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. II, 1, 81</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 4.1.149" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 149</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 5.122" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. V, 122</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 1.2.451" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. I, 2, 451</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 5.2.391" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 V, 2, 391</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 4.4.82" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. IV, 4, 82</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 2.1.310" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. II, 1, 310</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 3.3.165" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 165</bibl> <cit><quote>(the green-eyed monster).</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 3.3.165" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 165</bibl></cit> <bibl n="shak. oth 3.3.165" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 165</bibl> <bibl n="shak. oth 3.3.165" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 165</bibl> <bibl n="shak. oth 4.1.102" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 102</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 5.4.66" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 4, 66</bibl>. Plur. <cit><quote>--ies:</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.3.182" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 3, 182</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.2.164" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 164</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 5.5.139" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 5, 139</bibl> (Evans' speeches). <bibl n="shak. wt 3.2.114" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. III, 2, 114</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 3.2.114" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. III, 2, 114</bibl> <bibl n="shak. wt 4.1.18" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 18</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 4.3.90" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. IV, 3, 90</bibl>.<lb />2) suspicion in any way, apprehension: <cit><quote>j., that sour unwelcome guest,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 449" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 449</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>where love reigns, disturbing j. doth call himself affection's sentinel,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 449" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 449</bibl></cit> <cit><quote>j. itself could not mistrust,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 1516" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1516</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>to find out shames and idle hours in me, the scope and tenour of thy j.</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 61.8" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 61, 8</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>j. shall be called assurance,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 2.2.49" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado II, 2, 49</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>shuddering fear and green-eyed j.</quote> <bibl n="shak. mv 3.2.110" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. III, 2, 110</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>j. what might befall your travel,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tn 3.3.8" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. III, 3, 8</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. h5 2.2.126" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 II, 2, 126</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 2.1.113" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. II, 1, 113</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 4.5.19" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 5, 19</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 3.3.147" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. III, 3, 147</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 4.3.22" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. IV, 3, 22</bibl>. Plur.: <cit><quote>transported by my --ies,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 3.2.159" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. III, 2, 159</bibl></cit>. <emph>surmises, --ies, conjectures,</emph> H4B Ind. <bibl n="shak. wt 3.2.159" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. III, 2, 159</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mac 4.3.29" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. IV, 3, 29</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 2.2.134" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. II, 2, 134</bibl>. -- == <cit><quote>jealous,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.2.93" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. II, 2, 93</bibl></cit> (Mrs Quickly).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>